drm: msm: adreno: Use PTR_ERR_OR_ZERO rather than if(IS_ERR(...)) +PTR_ERR

Use PTR_ERR_OR_ZERO rather than if(IS_ERR(...)) + PTR_ERR because its
better to have inlined function rather than code-opened implementation.

